import './App.css';

import Header from './structure/header/header'
import Slider from './structure/slider/slider'
import Slider2 from './structure/slider/slider2'
import Contacts from './structure/contact/contact';
import{ Divider, DividerDown} from './structure/divider/divider';


import Education from './pages/education/education'
import Project from './pages/projects/projects'
import Banner from './structure/banner/banner';
import Contact from './pages/contact/contact'
import About from './pages/about/about'
import Home from './pages/home/home'


import{
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Routes,
  Route
}from "react-router-dom"

const App = () => (
<Router>
  <Banner/>
  {/* <Header
    titulo='David Pacheco'
    logo="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/518/518713.png"
  /> */}
  <Divider
    title='Habilidades'
  />
  <Slider/>
  <DividerDown/>
  <Divider
    title='Educacion'
  />
  <Slider2/>
  <DividerDown/>
  <Divider
    title='Sobre mi'
  />
  
  <DividerDown/>
  <Divider
    title='Contacto'
  />
  <Contacts/>
  <DividerDown/>
  <Routes>
    <Route path="/" element={<Home/>} />
    <Route path="" element={<Project/>} />
    <Route path="" element={<Education/>} />
    <Route path="" element={<About/>} />
    <Route path="" element={<Contact/>} />
  </Routes>
</Router>
)

export default App
